snippet.title: Tennis World Tour 2 | Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Take to the court in Tennis World Tour 2! We've rebuilt the game from the ground up, adding new animations, increasing the pace of the game, and offering players more opportunities to express their skill and score points. 
 
Pair up and compete in doubles matches, or opt-in for a short flurry of intense competition in Tie Break Tens. Prepare for the most comprehensive tennis experience yet, Tennis World Tour 2 will be coming to PC and consoles in 2020.

-------------------------------
